Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:49.02,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\b1\c&H786F5A&\frz0.6821\pos(685,310)\frx16\fry6}時間：剩餘36分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 詩音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩音？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:02:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩音姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(840,710)}詩音…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(362,710)}停
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才不是已經打過招呼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成你還有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…我只是想在正賽開始之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做些有意義的情報交換…之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你願意的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以是可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正到頭來也是我單方面的說明會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那種想法…我也不是沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.27,0:03:42.14,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs30}距離BOB正賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.27,0:03:42.14,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs30}時間：剩餘32分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問這次大會 您的狀態如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了緊要關頭我就用那個一決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正賽每次都是這樣熱鬧的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZXED用了我的情報正賽一定能有好排名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要確保勝利的話就用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位選手的絕密情報一份只要1000遊戲幣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗風 我可全賭你身上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,huuka的賠率是多少…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴因…雖然裝備和能力都不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過依舊老樣子表現平平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次估計也就15名左右的程度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說黑馬的話 我覺得賭力奇不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說誰表現平平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的我和以前可不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那個是小桐人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說是用光劍砍了不少人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷艷高貴的狂戰士嗎 好像很不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 果然還是小詩音好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也被小詩音射了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有點想被砍了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你還不如去ALO呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:04:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要幫我加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小…小桐人 要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把全部財產都賭你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…到底在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:12.23,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&HF7F7F7&\an2\fscx82\fscy87\pos(321,91)}m 400 3 l 800 3 800 100 400 100
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:12.23,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40\c&H2B2728&}距離BOB正賽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:12.23,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40\c&H302A2B&}時間：剩餘20分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說正賽中 30名玩家會被隨機傳送到同一張地圖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後進行遭遇戰 活到最後的就是勝利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道 結果還是想讓我來做說明嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且這些在運營商發來的郵件上全部都有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我姑且也看過了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…我想確認一下自己的理解有沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真敢說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上都和你剛才說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正賽是30名玩家在同一張地圖上的遭遇戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是隨機分配
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是每位玩家之間至少會有1000米的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1…1000米？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是說 地圖會非常寬廣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的有看過郵件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正賽地圖是直徑10Km的圓形地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由山脈 森林 沙漠等地形組成的復合地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間設定是下午開戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以也沒有裝備好壞而造成的不平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣真的可以遇上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是槍戰遊戲 所以這點距離還是有必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且參賽者都會被自動分配一個「衛星掃瞄器」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(932,670)}Satellite Scan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Satellite？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,間諜衛星那樣的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 設定上每隔15分鐘就會有監視衛星從上空經過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候 會向所有在場玩家發送玩家的位置情報
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 就是說在一個地點埋伏的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最多也不能超過15分鐘的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 有這樣的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對玩狙的不會很不利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一槍幹掉一個 然後轉移陣地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,15分鐘足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣吧 沒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次 找到你的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 等一下 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有其他事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來才是正題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…雖然是個很奇怪的問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在首次參加BOB的玩家裏 詩音不認識的人有幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？這算什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.81,0:07:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是名字的話倒是無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首次參賽的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了某個令人生氣的光劍使外 還有三人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三人？都叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銃士X和Pale Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有…這個是念Sterben嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「死槍」就在這些人之中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從剛才開始就什麼說明都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我差不多真的要生氣了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這算什麼 是想讓我生氣而在正賽裏失誤的計劃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你在昨天的預賽裏突然變得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天 我突然被之前玩過的VRMMO遊戲裏的玩家搭了話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕就是剛才幾個名字的其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該和他真正廝殺過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我甚至連他當時的名字都不記得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廝殺？敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…組隊的時候鬧矛盾…之類的理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是真正賭上了性命的廝殺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他…他所屬的集團
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯下了絕對不可饒恕的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和解已經不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以只能用劍來做個了結
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.12,0:09:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事本身我並不後悔 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我卻一直無視了自己理應背負的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強迫自己忘記 直到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 事情已經不允許我繼續逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次我必須真正面對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 說了奇怪的話 忘記這些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此你仍舊能扣得下扳機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那把槍的子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠殺死現實中的玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且不這麼做的話 自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者說某個非常重要的人就會被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種情況下 你仍舊能扣得下扳機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人…難道你在那個遊戲裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 這是不能問的問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…沒關繫了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.34,0:11:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩音？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該去等候室了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否則就沒時間檢查裝備和集中精力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我瞭解你也有你自己的苦衷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你和我的約定又是另一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天決賽上的那筆帳 我一定要討回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你要是被別的玩家幹掉 我一定不饒你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在遇到你之前我絕對會活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.79,0:12:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜歡槍油與硝煙味道的戰士們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬馬券押注的時間馬上就完了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 在VRMMO中難度最高的GGO的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最強玩家將在今晚揭曉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MMOStream將全程直播此次比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是！倒計時開始了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「最強決定戰」 開戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(573,670)}Bullet of Bullets
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,bingo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒！打得好啊詩音親
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還活著的有21人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dyne那邊被追著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利奇是用重機關鎗打梭子的打法 應該不會主動移動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要瞄的話應該選Dyne那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰要管那種傢伙啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娘的！搞什麼啊那傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧小子 趕緊滾出來 老子給你打成蜂窩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論何時都要「注意死角」哦 Dyne君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(671,670)}Check six
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:10.50,Warning,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(450,450)}Check six：航空用語 「注意6點方向（正後方，死角的意思）」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我有個提案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種情況下提案和妥協都不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有人會死！只是如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了！我不想被對方察覺到！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把在那個橋上的對戰看到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前你別出手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了 然後做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然會看情況 不過多半是我離開這
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會打你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能會從背後狙你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那樣的話我就認命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你吃了這提案 就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你重新振作的話 下次會好好跟我打？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:16:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好歹也警戒下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那傢伙打算跑路的話 我可會在他動之前開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬧哪樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我艸！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙 好強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠控制裝備重量來增強立體機動力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且「輕技」技能點得很高
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(558,670)}Acrobat
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娘的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有換彈夾的時間 還不如直接拿在腰間把子彈射光不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個藍色的 很強嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙就是那個披風裏頭的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是敵人 我和他應該實打實地廝殺過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙我要狙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果那傢伙是那個男人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想說他能在這點距離下躲過去？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽漏了槍聲？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 確實是我們沒聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能考慮的應該是槍聲小的光槍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是實彈槍的話應該有加消聲器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙應該還沒死才對 為什麼不想動了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是從森林那打的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.37,0:19:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我覺得應該是從更遠的敵方開槍狙的才對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.72,0:20:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才我看地圖的時候1km內沒人才對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來桐人！你又是從哪冒出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是追著那個叫Pale Rider的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 被掃瞄的時候我在順著那游的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在潛在水裏 所以沒被衛星掃到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你穿著裝備怎麼潛的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是把裝備全都脫下來丟到道具保管那了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一直躲在河裏就不會被「衛星掃瞄器」捕捉到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(786,670)}Satellite Scan
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先記著了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩音 在那傢伙的角色上出現了奇怪的閃光特效
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電擊彈？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.45,0:21:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從什麼時候就在那了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「沉默的暗殺者」？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(618,670)}SilentAssassin
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:17.00,Warning,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(450,450)\fs28}SilentAssassin：AMP/AMW（L96A1）的衍生型 這裏叫的是英軍裏用的「沉默的暗殺者（SilentAssassin）」這個外號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把步槍的名字嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝備有標準型消聲器的高性能狙擊槍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然聽過在GGO裏存在的傳聞 我還是頭一次見到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能用那種槍 那傢伙何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想用手槍了結了他？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩音 開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.55,0:21:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？打哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:21:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打那個破披風的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了！狙了他！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.16,0:22:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他開槍之前！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下話 死槍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=========================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:08.10,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}もっと強く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.20,0:22:13.13,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}そう、強くなりたいと願った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:16.82,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,525)}悲しみを超えて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:31.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}変わることない過去に何度も背を向けてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.44,0:22:38.72,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}誰にも見せられない傷を隠したまま ずっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.89,0:22:42.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}溢れだしたこの痛みは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.44,0:22:45.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}全て一人で抱きしめる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.02,0:22:48.84,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}いつか消える温もりなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.90,0:22:53.56,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}一つもいらないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.66,0:22:56.48,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}もっと強く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.55,0:23:01.39,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}そう、強くなりたいと願った
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.44,0:23:07.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}暗闇をかける孤独な星のように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:15.70,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}心深く沈めた弱くて脆い自分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:19.30,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}言葉にできなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.36,0:23:22.60,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}声にもならなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.69,0:23:27.82,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}きっと誰にも見つからないように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.89,0:23:33.04,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,825)}ただ 、光を待ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:08.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}更加堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.20,0:22:13.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}沒錯 我祈願能變得更加堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:16.82,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,525)}去超越悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:31.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}對著一成不變的過去 無數次轉過身去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.44,0:22:38.72,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}藏著無法給任何人看的傷疤 一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.89,0:22:42.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}溢出來的這份傷痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.44,0:22:45.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}全都自己抱著不放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.02,0:22:48.84,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}如果是終有一天會消失的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.90,0:22:53.56,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}寧肯一個都不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.66,0:22:56.48,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}更加堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.55,0:23:01.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}沒錯 我祈願能變得更加堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.44,0:23:07.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}就如同那在黑暗上馳騁的孤獨的星塵一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:15.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}在內心深處躲避著的脆弱的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:19.30,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}無法言語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.36,0:23:22.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}也無法叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.69,0:23:27.82,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,225)}一定正不讓任何人察覺到地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.89,0:23:33.04,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(225,825)}悄悄地等待著光明
